---
import LegalLayout from '../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
---
<LegalLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How Revvia collects, uses, and protects the information you share with us."
  path="/privacy"
>
  <p>Revvia ("we," "us") operates this website. This policy explains what we collect and how we use it. By using the site you agree to this policy.</p>

  <h2>Information we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Information you give us:</strong> when you submit the Growth Audit form or subscribe, we collect your name, business name, email, store URL, budget range, contact preference, and any message you send.</li>
    <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> we use Google Analytics 4 and the Meta Pixel to understand how the site is used. These set cookies and collect anonymized usage data. Our default consent posture denies advertising storage; analytics is used in aggregate.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How we use it</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To respond to your inquiry and prepare your growth audit.</li>
    <li>To improve the site and measure marketing performance in aggregate.</li>
    <li>We do <strong>not</strong> sell your personal information.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Form submissions</h2>
  <p>Form submissions are processed by Netlify Forms and may be routed to our team's email and an internal Google Sheet. We retain submissions only as long as needed to follow up.</p>

  <h2>Your choices</h2>
  <p>You can decline cookies through your browser settings and unsubscribe from emails at any time. To request access to or deletion of your data, email <a href="mailto:info@revvia.com">info@revvia.com</a>.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Revvia (First Door, LLC), 5927 Priestly Drive, Suite 212, Carlsbad, CA 92008. Email <a href="mailto:info@revvia.com">info@revvia.com</a>, phone <a href="tel:+17607822875">(760) 782-2875</a>.</p>
</LegalLayout>
